data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Seller is offering up to $10,000 in closing costs with acceptable offer! Use towards a new roof, closing costs or to buy down your interest rate! Existing VA loan at 4.75% is assumable for both military and non-military buyers who plan to use as primary residence.     Welcome to your dream home in the desirable Fairways Lake Estates community! This stunning solar powered single family pool home boasts 1,638 sqft of living space, featuring 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 well-appointed bathrooms. Situated just off of Hwy 27 and US 192. Only minutes from Disney World, this home is ideal for use as a vacation home or primary residence.    As you enter, you will be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere of the open floor plan. The kitchen has been recently remodeled with high-end cabinets and gorgeous granite counters. The gas range is perfect for the home chef. The extended breakfast bar is great for casual dining and entertaining.    The living room is bright and airy, with large windows allowing for natural light to fill the space. Sliding glass doors lead to the private enclosed in-ground pool, with views of the golf course, providing the perfect spot for relaxing and soaking up the Florida sunshine.    The master suite is a true retreat, featuring a spacious layout, walk-in closet, and a wonderfully appointed en-suite bathroom. The remaining two bedrooms are generously sized and share a lovely guest bathroom.    Enjoy the benefits of living in a golf community, with access to a variety of amenities including a golf course, clubhouse, and tennis courts. Additionally, the community provides access to Old Lake Davenport for fishing and boating, making this the perfect spot for water enthusiasts.    Schedule a showing today and start living the Florida lifestyle you've been dreaming of.
